title.rendered: India vs Australia: Virat Kohli’s Reaction To Umesh Yadav Being Hit For Boundaries Becomes An Instant Meme

content.rendered:
Chasing 209 for a win, Australia overhauled the target with 4 balls to spare against host India in Mohali on Tuesday. During the Australia’s innings, Umesh Yadav bowled the second over and Cameron Green (61 off 30) got stuck into him, hitting four boundaries off his first four deliveries. As the lanky all-rounder opening the batting for Australia, slammed the second delivery for a boundary, meanwhile the camera caught the animated Virat Kohli with worried expression like meme-worthy.

The former West Indies pacer tweeted over Kohli’s reaction, I can see that Virat Kohli look becoming a meme.

Virat Kohli
